{"tid":1437974,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[重開] 香港人抗爭Calendar 上線啦","createTime":"2019-08-09T16:12:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T07:39:36.000Z","uid":281928,"like":59,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"f2dd4a7bfaa32c9dff7356b460196b5c295dd522","tid":1437974,"uid":281928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:12:12.000Z","msg":"(重開: 已fix 網頁版link手機上會404問題)<br />\n<br />\n眼見香港人每個星期都有唔同嘅抗爭活動，上環，中環，旺角，尖沙咀，有時想搵返下個weekend有咩活動都唔容易！<br />\n<br />\n有見及此，我地團隊整咗個google public calendar，希望整合各個活動。<br />\n可能大家未必好知public calendar 係咩黎，其實係公司日常運作會用得多啲，要黎睇幾時有meeting之類。<br />\n<br />\n係一個你只需要subscribe，你就可以係你電話日曆上睇到最新日程！<br />\n<br />\n<ins>先出結果：</ins><br />\n<br />\n網頁版 / Google calendar：<br />\n<a href=\"https://cutt.ly/4wyEXIH\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcutt.ly%2F4wyEXIH&d=Zo4i0ptUI%2BsV2bg8TrofrEzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=99e3264a\" target=\"_blank\">https://cutt.ly/4wyEXIH</a><br />\n<br />\n(原link: <a href=\"https://calendar.google.com/calendar/embed?src=hkcampaignschedule%40gmail.com&amp;ctz=Asia%2FHong_Kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcalendar.google.com%2Fcalendar%2Fembed%3Fsrc%3Dhkcampaignschedule%2540gmail.com%26ctz%3DAsia%252FHong_Kong&d=Zo4i0ptUI%2BsV2bg8TrofrEzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=e830077f\" target=\"_blank\">https://calendar.google.com/calendar/embed?src=hkcampaignschedule%40gmail.com&amp;ctz=Asia%2FHong_Kong</a>)<br />\n<br />\niPhone版：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7CM0uHo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7CM0uHo.png&h=1c380f01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins>咁到底點set up呢？</ins><br />\n如果你係用Google calendar，只需要係網頁版嘅右下角㩒個+制<br />\n<br />\n如果係iPhone 用家， 就要subscribe 依個calendar啦<br />\nSettings -&gt; Passwords &amp; Accounts -&gt; Add Account -&gt; Other -&gt; Add Subscribed Calendar<br />\n(之後有step by step圖)<br />\n<br />\n然後copy and paste依條link: <br />\n<a href=\"https://calendar.google.com/calendar/ical/hkcampaignschedule%40gmail.com/public/basic.ics\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcalendar.google.com%2Fcalendar%2Fical%2Fhkcampaignschedule%2540gmail.com%2Fpublic%2Fbasic.ics&d=Zo4i0ptUI%2BsV2bg8TrofrEzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=e71da1a5\" target=\"_blank\">https://calendar.google.com/calendar/ical/hkcampaignschedule%40gmail.com/public/basic.ics</a><br />\n<br />\n現階段我地主要靠各個公開渠道得知event，會盡力確保齊備，如果有遺留既日程，歡迎告知！"},{"pid":"770b6731347f19c783800142d4292b7be6709fc5","tid":1437974,"uid":281928,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:13:12.000Z","msg":"1. Passwords &amp; Accounts<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9GLgNyy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9GLgNyy.png&h=ceb7212d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2. Add Account<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kzKhw1O.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkzKhw1O.png&h=1de9ec12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n3. Other<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VK4ELmP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVK4ELmP.png&h=6112d828&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n4. Add Subscribed Calendar<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c7j9n8w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc7j9n8w.png&h=cf85c233&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n5. Copy and paste 條link:<br />\n<a href=\"https://calendar.google.com/calendar/ical/hkcampaignschedule%40gmail.com/public/basic.ics\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcalendar.google.com%2Fcalendar%2Fical%2Fhkcampaignschedule%2540gmail.com%2Fpublic%2Fbasic.ics&d=Zo4i0ptUI%2BsV2bg8TrofrEzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=e71da1a5\" target=\"_blank\">https://calendar.google.com/calendar/ical/hkcampaignschedule%40gmail.com/public/basic.ics</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s9RosAB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs9RosAB.png&h=928287bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n6. 最後㩒Next就搞掂<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TvO6qn1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTvO6qn1.png&h=4af015b4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5c18dc4fe8bc9401be0fe91650889c221b2eed92","tid":1437974,"uid":281928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:13:46.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"709bcf38c6511e44c6de085cfedda390544d0766","tid":1437974,"uid":73826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:14:22.000Z","msg":"PUSHHHHHH<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ccfb011b695019d877c2906a64568ec8e57755e","tid":1437974,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:16:43.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"d5762fed6758d12107e76cf5541dccfd5ff6c388","tid":1437974,"uid":281928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:18:32.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2984e08fa2012763c88930c1fc57ae670c2609ce","tid":1437974,"uid":281928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:20:20.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f52c1e7389a4d88b5ea17cddc41c6c550d29c751","tid":1437974,"uid":281928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:30:26.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e3c9853ff90201cd258fa75dab012b574d4c94d9","tid":1437974,"uid":281928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:31:51.000Z","msg":"有用到既手足可以講聲，我地連有幾多人subscribe 都睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e365c05d6836ec6280245d9f9ae8c5e708ad84d6","tid":1437974,"uid":281928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:37:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a133655d0c8482a9d1a8573561226bd2d000f8f","tid":1437974,"u