rc%3Dhkcampaignschedule%2540gmail.com%26ctz%3DAsia%252FHong_Kong&d=Zo4i0ptUI%2BsV2bg8TrofrEzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=e830077f\" target=\"_blank\">https://calendar.google.com/calendar/embed?src=hkcampaignschedule%40gmail.com&amp;ctz=Asia%2FHong_Kong</a>)<br />\n<br />\niPhone版：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7CM0uHo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7CM0uHo.png&h=1c380f01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins>咁到底點set up呢？</ins><br />\n如果你係用Google calendar，只需要係網頁版嘅右下角㩒個+制<br />\n<br />\n如果係iPhone 用家， 就要subscribe 依個calendar啦<br />\nSettings -&gt; Passwords &amp; Accounts -&gt; Add Account -&gt; Other -&gt; Add Subscribed Calendar<br />\n(之後有step by step圖)<br />\n<br />\n然後copy and paste依條link: <br />\n<a href=\"https://calendar.google.com/calendar/ical/hkcampaignschedule%40gmail.com/public/basic.ics\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcalendar.google.com%2Fcalendar%2Fical%2Fhkcampaignschedule%2540gmail.com%2Fpublic%2Fbasic.ics&d=Zo4i0ptUI%2BsV2bg8TrofrEzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=e71da1a5\" target=\"_blank\">https://calendar.google.com/calendar/ical/hkcampaignschedule%40gmail.com/public/basic.ics</a><br />\n<br />\n現階段我地主要靠各個公開渠道得知event，會盡力確保齊備，如果有遺留既日程，歡迎告知！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:45:10.000Z","msg":"iPhone 唔撚洗咁煩，直接開link 禁兩個掣搞掂"},{"pid":"03de2ef794a4fa42672e3fde2dd287aef23d80c6","tid":1437974,"uid":83232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:46:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99f9a038fbeb9462e3cde2aed2b048a08455e02c","tid":1437974,"uid":281928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e22491d99435630003338c815ea07d58bce1e992","tid":1437974,"uid":185449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f2dd4a7bfaa32c9dff7356b460196b5c295dd522","tid":1437974,"uid":281928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:12:12.000Z","msg":"(重開: 已fix 網頁版link手機上會404問題)<br />\n<b