果有遺留既日程，歡迎告知！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:45:10.000Z","msg":"iPhone 唔撚洗咁煩，直接開link 禁兩個掣搞掂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T06:56:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b378e532b91a4ed5dd0ef34322166907ed2380f","tid":1437974,"uid":131842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T06:57:02.000Z","msg":"大埔@1455 <a href=\"https://hkmap.live/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkmap.live%2F&d=Zo4i0ptUI%2BsV2bg8TrofrEzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=dacb7248\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkmap.live/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HntN1s5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHntN1s5.png&h=8e964082&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n[長期置頂] [iOS/Android/PC/Mac] 香城online正式加入地圖功能<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1438115\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1438115</a>"},{"pid":"8edf77efdba7773973fc93981a1a2f5e4977f201","tid":1437974,"uid":281928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b378e532b91a4ed5dd0ef34322166907ed2380f","tid":1437974,"uid":131842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T06:57:02.000Z","msg":"大埔@1455 <a href=\"https://hkmap.live/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkmap.live%2F&d=Zo4i0ptUI%2BsV2bg8TrofrEzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=dacb7248\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkmap.live/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HntN1s5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHntN1s5.png&h=8e964082&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n[長期置頂] [iOS/Android/PC/Mac] 香城online正式加入地圖功能<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1438115\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1438115</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T07:02:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2f40e5b6d6a0675e5db4bd5e68fc2d3907fbaf1","tid":1437974,"uid":281928,"like":0,"di